arts.ttl: Jordan Henderson dragged away by Ajax stars during angry mid-game row with team-mate
arts.sum: Jordan Henderson has endured a frustrating season in Ajax and tempers flared on Thursday night when he confronted team-mate Bertrand Traore during a win over Besiktas

arts.ttl: Ajax sweep aside Besiktas in the Europa League
arts.sum: Ajax got their Europa League campaign off to a fine start with a comfortable 4-0 win over Besiktas in Amsterdam. Besiktas had been unbeaten under Giovanni van Bronckhorst until they arrived in Amsterdam but Ajax played them off the park with an energetic display.
